name: GDSC-LAUNCH-GAME2
description:
Embark on a fun arcade-ish story on how Delta transformed themselves to Google Developers Student Club!

Various Milestones had to be met such as Lead Selection , Finding Domains , Core Team formation , Website Development and of course the Launch!

Let's see if you can overcome the Trials presented by game in order to get access to join the GDSC Chapter!

Take that Leap of Faith and Join Us!!

PLEASE NOTE:

Please use Google Chrome for Best experience!

Please make sure that AdBlockers are turned off while playing this game.

Please do NOT play the game in incognito Mode.
